lines.text: The mine-working hie north of the town , "
said Dan . " If we head west we ought to
cut the trail leading from Gilbury to the north . "
So we swung west, making slow going over
rough county , sliding on shale , climbing down
auto draws, arching a big mysa by a
pour or five mile vally , sandy-florced . It
gut haller as the day were on and he rested
gratefuly by a small seek where he watered
the harses and drank enough to cure
